## Layer Summary

| Layer | Files | Technology |
|-------|-------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | `talk2data/src/` | React, Redux, SSE |
| **Backend Gateway** | `backend_server.py` | FastAPI, LangChain callbacks |
| **Supervisor Agent** | `agents/supervisor_agent.py` | LangChain, Groq `llama-3.3-70b` |
| **Tool Layer** | `tools/*.py` | LangChain `@tool` decorators |
| **MCP Tool Server** | `mcp_server.py` | FastAPI on port 8000 |
| **Search Service** | `services/search_service.py` | BM25, FAISS, Node2Vec, RRF |
| **LLM Service** | `services/llm_service.py` | Groq SDK (fast + smart models) |
| **Execution** | `tools/malloy_executor_tool.py` | Groq LLM + `mysql-connector` |
| **Semantic Schema** | `models/fmcg.malloy` | Malloy DSL |
| **Databases** | MySQL + Neo4j | `fmcg_database`, graph relations |
| **Observability** | Phoenix on port 6006 | OpenTelemetry / OTLP |
| **Config** | `.env`, `utils/config.py` | Environment variables |

