## LLM Usage Map

| Task | Model | Where |
|------|-------|-------|
| Intent extraction | `llama-3.1-8b-instant` (fast) | `llm_service.extract_intent()` |
| Malloy generation | `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` (smart) | `llm_service.generate_malloy()` |
| Malloy → SQL translation | `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` (smart) | `malloy_executor_tool.translate_malloy_to_sql()` |
| Agent reasoning | `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` (smart) | `supervisor_agent.py` |

